aris\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 228}, {\"ngram\": \"Zonewill\", \"from\": 239, \"to\": 247}, {\"ngram\": \"7 am\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 280}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 305, \"to\": 309}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Collinsworth, co-host of NBC'sFootball Night in Americafrom on-location each weekand a play-by-play announcer for NBC Sports' college football and basketball coverage, returns for his third NBC Olympics assignment.\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 437, \"end\": 447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.7936454350068125, \"rank\": 0.2600054510958654, \"text\": \"NBC Sports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 513, \"end\": 525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"co\", \"from\": 337, \"to\": 339}, {\"ngram\": \"host\", \"from\": 340, \"to\": 344}, {\"ngram\": \"NBC'sFootball Night\", \"from\": 348, \"to\": 367}, {\"ngram\": \"Americafrom\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 382}, {\"ngram\": \"location\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 394}, {\"ngram\": \"play\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 422}, {\"ngram\": \"basketball coverage\", \"from\": 470, \"to\": 489}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Previously, he served as a social media correspondent at the 2016 Rio Games and as an on-location contributor to Peacock'sTokyo Tonightshow at the Tokyo Games.\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 697, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a social media correspondent\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 591}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2016 Rio Games\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 613}, {\"ngram\": \"location\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 635}, {\"ngram\": \"Peacock'sTokyo\", \"f