ily offering will provide viewers with the most comprehensive and all-encompassing live whip-around coverage of any Olympic Games to date.\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 1350, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The daily live show\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 976}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 992}, {\"ngram\": \"the excitement\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1015}, {\"ngram\": \"triumphs\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1025}, {\"ngram\": \"emotion\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1038}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1051}, {\"ngram\": \"all the events\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1076}, {\"ngram\": \"viewers\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1104}, {\"ngram\": \"the most exhilarating moments\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1139}, {\"ngram\": \"key races\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1153}, {\"ngram\": \"routines\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1163}, {\"ngram\": \"Gold Zone's daily offering\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1224}, {\"ngram\": \"viewers\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1245}, {\"ngram\": \"the most comprehensive and all-encompassing live whip-around coverage\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1320}, {\"ngram\": \"any Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1341}, {\"ngram\": \"date\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1349}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Collinsworth replacesAkbar Gbajabiamila, who can no longer hostGold Zonedue to a scheduling conflict.\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1452, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Collinsworth replacesAkbar Gbajabiamila\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1390}, {\"ngram\": \"Zonedue\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1426}, {\"ngram\": \"a scheduling conflict\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The hosts will often be joined by special guests throughout the day.Gold Zonewill also be available on NBCSports.com and the NBC Sports app via \\\"TV Everywhere\\\" for customers with pay-TV subscriptions.\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1557, \"end\": 1570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCSports.com\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 1579, \"end\": 1589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.7936454350068125, \"rank\": 0.2600054510958654, \"text\": \"NBC Sports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The hosts\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1463}, {\"ngram\": \"special guests\", \"from\": 1488, \"to\": 1502}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1514, \"to\": 1521}, {\"ngram\": \"Gold Zonewill\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1535}, {\"ngram\": \"TV Everywhere\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1612}, {\"ngram\": \"customers\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1627}, {\"ngram\": \"pay-TV subscriptions\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1653}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peacock will be the streaming home of the 2024 Paris Olympics, providing fans with the most comprehensive Olympic destination in U.S. media history.\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1804, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peacock\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1663}, {\"ngram\": \"the streaming home\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1690}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1717}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1733}, {\"ngram\": \"the most comprehensive Olympic destination\", \"from\": 1739, \"to\": 1781}, {\"ngram\": \"U.S. media history\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a Summer Games first for Peacock, it will stream every sport and event, including all 329 medal events, and will feature full-event replays; all NBC programming; curated video clips; virtual channels; exclusive original programming; and more.\", \"from\": 1805, \"to\": 2050, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1953, \"end\": 1956, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\":